&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a band 4 Nurse Associate or Assistant practitioner to work in a busy medical ward at Wigan, Royal Albert Edward Infirmary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an enthusiastic, self motivated, forward thinking individual who will be committed to providing high quality care to our patients with both acute and chronic medical conditions in a very friendly environment, with much focus on learning, support and developement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is a fixed term until March 2022 position and is for 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All candidates will be required to show evidence of their original certificates to the interview panel.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
